    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/bc08ccb64c9fd19199aadbe27be8b7ee.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=800 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/bc08ccb64c9fd19199aadbe27be8b7ee.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/5a2f1435cc7bafb835a133e1e36414d5.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/5a2f1435cc7bafb835a133e1e36414d5.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/5a2f1435cc7bafb835a133e1e36414d5.mp4?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And repeat... <strong>Or die trying</strong>.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources are scarce, but the seeds of your salvation lie scattered beyond your farm. Venture into the Calamity, battle vicious creatures, and claim rare seeds guarded by fang and claw. Plant them. Harvest them. Grow stronger with every season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is <strong>FARMCORE</strong> gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/e1ca427b1ce7f4758e77b4d3cd4aee95.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=800 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/e1ca427b1ce7f4758e77b4d3cd4aee95.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/e2daa6ed89382c52268b0820af128650.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/e2daa6ed89382c52268b0820af128650.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/e2daa6ed89382c52268b0820af128650.mp4?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;You've been kept from <strong>the truth</strong>.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An isolated girl, finally freed from her mother's imprisonment and experimentations, discovers an irradiated wasteland brimming with colossal mechanisms and constructs, unexplainable magical artifacts, and horrific feral creatures that want nothing more than to erase her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Succumbing to the horrors means going back, and that's a fate <i>worse than death</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/f07ed0abbee748c9b8d109c8c5b3f291.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=800 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/f07ed0abbee748c9b8d109c8c5b3f291.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/87bf973a70109a09bbda82019d5b050e.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/87bf973a70109a09bbda82019d5b050e.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/87bf973a70109a09bbda82019d5b050e.mp4?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wield the scythe not just to reap, <strong>but to rise</strong>.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your scythe is more than just your primary weapon and farming tool, it's your fast and fluid way to navigate through the Calamity. Slice through the air with the <i>SCYTHE-DASH</i> action to weave through hordes of enemies, ascend the shattered landscapes, and ride raw momentum back to the safety of your farm with spoils in hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/79afa9431b8a753e3af298369cc05061.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=800 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/79afa9431b8a753e3af298369cc05061.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/927c7f4771a23f8ecc2737393c90bdf3.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=616 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/927c7f4771a23f8ecc2737393c90bdf3.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/927c7f4771a23f8ecc2737393c90bdf3.mp4?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Seemingly harmless creatures... but <strong>what motivates them</strong>?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/0ca617215671d0f5215d39c82ba0d26b.poster.avif?t=1771920522\" width=800 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045340/extras/0ca617215671d0f5215d39c82ba0d26b.webm?t=1771920522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable weapons, player builds, and playstyles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up and repair your farmland to permanently increase your powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soar through the skies using momentum based movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the dark and twisted secrets hidden across the Calamity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing. 🎣</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>There's still a way out, but it won't be easy.</strong></h2>",
